From 6377f15deb8b5f4c01cca37fbc88e835ff7352b3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: deceptech-packet-ninja <roland.blandon@packetninjas.net>
Date: Mon, 30 Mar 2026 14:01:59 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] feat: add --kv-bits, --turbo-kv-bits, /debug/memory,
 /debug/clear_cache to server

Enables KV cache quantization and TurboQuant in mlx_lm.server.
Batching disabled when kv_bits or turbo_kv_bits is set.
Adds /debug/memory GET endpoint for MLX memory diagnostics.
Adds /debug/clear_cache POST endpoint to free MLX buffer cache.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
